f=Engineering/ops/custom/incident-response/assets/postmortem-template.md · h1:Post-Mortem [incident id] [date]=Blameless: name systems, conditions, decisions never culprits. Incomplete until Feeds section done. Structure adapted credit SRE convention (marketplace: sre-incident-response) bound department's annealing loop. · s=**Severity:** P[0-3] **User impact:** [what users experienced, many, long], **Duration:** detected [t] mitigated [t] resolved [t] · h2:Timeline (facts only, timestamped)=\| Time \| What happened / what was done \| Source \| · h2:Timeline (facts only, timestamped)=\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Timeline (facts only, timestamped)=\| \| \| \| · h2:Contributing factors (systems, saints)=[factor condition/design/process allowed this; names-as-causes] · wh:worked / what failed=**Worked:** [detection, rollback, comms keep doing], **Failed missing:** [gaps becomes action item feed] · h2:Rail check=Data changes during mitigation: [none operator-run script refs Rail held, Any off-plan action: [none halt record ref] · h2:Feeds (MANDATORY post-mortem incomplete without these)=quinn regression-map entry: [RM-ref] written why-not: ___, dev ADR (if design flaw exposed): [ref n.a. because ___], maintenance-hygiene: baseline/alert updates: [refs none needed because ___], Recurrence check: prior incidents fragility? [none refs escalate dev] · h2:Action items=\| Item \| Owner \| Due \| Done \| · h2:Action items=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Action items=\| \| \| \| \|